Package com.group12.entity

Class OnlineGame

java.lang.Object
com.group12.entity.OnlineGame
public class OnlineGame extends Object
The OnlineGame class represents the state of an online game session. It holds information about the players, the turn count, the longest road length, and the longest road user.
